{
  "stem": "6076.6",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Now, I says-- now, she says, my dear sister, would you like to know my life story?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I didn't say nothing.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She says, yes I tell you.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I tell you my [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I tell you my life.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I started to cry and cry and cry when she told me that when they evacuated [INAUDIBLE], she with her husband, and with the two little girls were trying to build a bunker in their own house, underneath in the kitchen.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they were thinking maybe they will survive after the evacuation, maybe [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But how long can you sit in a bunker like that?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They sat for two week.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they decided, after two weeks, to go out and to seek for some foods, to ask, to go to, to a, to a, to these people, Polish, the Polish people, with whom they left all their goods.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because they owned textile, you know, business.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They left a lot of goods with them before the evacuation.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So they said, maybe they can give us some bread, some water, some whatever.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So [INAUDIBLE] her husband says, listen, Tobcha, my dear, I will walk out with Rachel hand by hand first.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You will stay with Chajale.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Hold on your arm behind the gate.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "If you hear something, some flick, [INAUDIBLE] goes on, if you hear some noise, go back to the bunker.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Perhaps you will have a better chance.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And soon when [INAUDIBLE] walks out with Rachel, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] this German [INAUDIBLE] was standing right on the corner.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he says, halt.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's all what Tobcha heard and a loud noise, the bullet.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because she was unaware.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He fell on the ground-- she didn't see him fell-- with her, with Rachel.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
